/****** Object:  Database [LHC]    Script Date: 2022/4/28 20:16:31 ******/
CREATE DATABASE [LHC]
 CONTAINMENT = NONE
 ON  PRIMARY 
( NAME = N'LHC', FILENAME = N'D:\DATA\LHC.mdf' , SIZE = 1872896KB , MAXSIZE = UNLIMITED, FILEGROWTH = 1024KB )
 LOG ON 
( NAME = N'LHC_log', FILENAME = N'D:\DATA\LHC_log.ldf' , SIZE = 326848KB , MAXSIZE = 2048GB , FILEGROWTH = 10%)
GO
